748
3017
00:59:08,550 --> 00:59:10,300
But

749
3021
00:59:12,480 --> 00:59:16,850
you do know. So that Ji Ho...

750
3025
00:59:17,560 --> 00:59:21,340
How to help Ji Ho to not give up on her dream.

751
3029
00:59:24,880 --> 00:59:29,920
So that is why you came to see me.

752
3033
00:59:29,920 --> 00:59:34,070
To an old lover who you met after 12 years,

753
3037
00:59:34,070 --> 00:59:36,610
