767
3093
01:00:36,010 --> 01:00:38,410
<i>"Although Nothing Changes If You Cry About It" by Poet Park Joon</i>

768
3097
01:00:40,740 --> 01:00:44,720
<i>But some words don't die</i>

769
3101
01:00:44,720 --> 01:00:46,110
