845
3405
01:05:24,600 --> 01:05:29,490
The wife taking care of these things behind the scenes is important, too.

846
3409
01:05:31,510 --> 01:05:32,990
Let's go now.

847
3413
01:05:32,990 --> 01:05:35,140
Wait, Father-in-law.

848
3417
01:05:40,550 --> 01:05:43,370
I have something to say to you.

849
3421
01:05:43,980 --> 01:05:46,480
It's cold, so careful going back.

850
3425
01:06:07,480 --> 01:06:09,520
Where are you? Why aren't you coming?

851
3429
01:06:09,520 --> 01:06:11,660
Oh, I'll be coming in a bit.

852
3433
01:06:11,660 --> 01:06:13,900
