858
3457
01:06:29,450 --> 01:06:31,050
Tada.

859
3461
01:06:36,800 --> 01:06:40,930
Soo Ji. You know the movie, "The Graduate," right?

860
3465
01:06:40,930 --> 01:06:44,800
