862
3473
01:06:48,100 --> 01:06:51,300
I saw it for the first time when I was a first-year in high school.

863
3477
01:06:51,300 --> 01:06:55,690
When Benjamin barged into Elaine's wedding

864
3481
01:06:55,690 --> 01:06:59,430
