865
3485
01:06:59,430 --> 01:07:02,090
How should I say it?

866
3489
01:07:02,090 --> 01:07:06,670
To my seventeen-year-old eyes, that seemed so romantic.

867
3493
01:07:06,670 --> 01:07:10,760
That's a famous scene. Lots of parodies were made of it, too.

868
3497
01:07:10,760 --> 01:07:12,980
But . . .

869
3501
01:07:12,980 --> 01:07:19,090
After I was over 20, I saw it again, and I noticed something different.

870
3505
01:07:21,260 --> 01:07:23,430
What?

871
3509
01:07:23,430 --> 01:07:26,100
The two's expressions afterward.

872
3513
01:07:28,580 --> 01:07:34,200
After they fled excitedly from the wedding, they rode the bus.

873
3517
01:07:35,150 --> 01:07:38,100
But strangely, the two have no words to say to each other.

874
3521
01:07:39,210 --> 01:07:43,140
Feeling anxious and empty.

875
3525
01:07:43,140 --> 01:07:46,080
I didn't notice that when I was young,

876
3529
01:07:47,860 --> 01:07:51,320
but I started to notice that scene at some point.

877
3533
01:07:55,330 --> 01:07:57,390
Why?

878
3537
01:07:57,390 --> 01:08:02,180
You see that scene between you and your landlord?

879
3541
01:08:10,610 --> 01:08:12,440
Are you having a hard time?

880
3545
01:08:18,210 --> 01:08:19,910
Yeah.

881
3549
01:08:36,500 --> 01:08:38,150
Yup.

882
3553
01:08:39,090 --> 01:08:40,730
Now?

883
3557
01:08:41,630 --> 01:08:43,530
Alright.

884
3561
01:08:45,900 --> 01:08:48,450
It's so cold.

885
3565
01:08:48,450 --> 01:08:50,560
Hurry and go on.

886
3569
01:08:51,250 --> 01:08:54,030
Nah. Why?

887
3573
01:08:54,030 --> 01:08:57,330
Hurry and go. CEO Ma's waiting.

888
3577
01:08:57,330 --> 01:09:00,880
Then, call me after you've arrived. Okay?

889
3581
01:09:15,670 --> 01:09:20,830
