890
3585
01:09:20,830 --> 01:09:23,230
Did you do something to Deputy Park?

891
3589
01:09:23,230 --> 01:09:27,490
Your way didn't work so this time, so this time, I did it my way.

892
3593
01:09:27,490 --> 01:09:29,660
Your way, what?

893
3597
01:09:29,660 --> 01:09:32,270
I punched him hard in his stupid mouth.

894
3601
01:09:33,330 --> 01:09:35,270
What?

895
3605
01:09:35,270 --> 01:09:36,870
<i>You did good. Good job! </i>

896
3609
01:09:36,870 --> 01:09:38,540
<i>Come here!</i>

897
3613
01:09:40,760 --> 01:09:42,200
<i>Hey!</i>

898
3617
01:09:46,140 --> 01:09:49,350
<i>Ack.</i>

899
3621
01:09:49,350 --> 01:09:52,700
<i>I only knew after love existed, </i>

900
3625
01:09:52,700 --> 01:09:55,930
<i>the reason our marriage was easy </i>

901
3629
01:09:56,930 --> 01:10:00,440
<i>was because there was no love. </i>

902
3633
01:10:00,440 --> 01:10:03,580
<i>I'll pay for half of your wedding attire cost.</i>

903
3637
01:10:03,580 --> 01:10:06,650
<i>No, it's alright. It's not that much anyway. </i>

904
3641
01:10:06,650 --> 01:10:09,880
<i>But you had to pay for wedding shoes and the bouquet, unlike me.</i>

905
3645
01:10:09,880 --> 01:10:13,400
<i>So I'll deduct them from next month's rent. </i>

906
3649
01:10:13,400 --> 01:10:16,870
<i>Marriage is supposed to be done out of love.</i>

907
3653
01:10:16,870 --> 01:10:19,040
<i>But why . . .</i>

908
3657
01:10:21,140 --> 01:10:24,700
<i>Then what about kids? When will you have a baby then?</i>

909
3661
01:10:25,830 --> 01:10:28,640
<i>After there is love, </i>

910
3665
01:10:28,640 --> 01:10:32,360
<i>why is it that the wounds just get bigger?</i>

911
